ANSIBLE ROLES: 

HANDS ON: 

create an role called sonarqube

ansible-galaxy role init sonarqube 

create ansible role for apache-maven

ansible-galaxy role init apache-maven

 ANSIBLE DRY RUN COMMAND: 
   --check
This command is used to run a playbook without actually executing the taks

ansible-playbook demo.yaml -i inventory --check. 

Testing the playbook: especially when working in production environment. 
